testCase.name: Create App Links Operation should create app links
Create App Links Operation should not create app links if the app name already exists
Create App Links Operation should not create app links if the app name is missing
Create App Links Operation should not create app links if the app url is missing
Create App Links Operation should not create app links if the app icon is missing
Create App Links Operation should not create app links if the app name is empty
Create App Links Operation should not create app links if the app url is empty
Create App Links Operation should not create app links if the app icon is empty
Create App Links Operation should return unauthorized if the user is not logged in
Create App Links Operation should return unauthorized with invalid token
Create App Links Operation should return bad request for invalid user input
